ywords" (Williams 1983; Striphas 2015; Thylstrup et al. 2021) for the study of culture, society, data.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aAnthologiesxHistory. 4aFilm, Media, and Communication. 4aMedia Studies. 4aScience and Technology. 7aCOMPUTERS / Database Management / Data Mining.2bisacsh  aanthology, streaming platforms, recommendation systems, algorithmic culture.40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048554591?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048554591zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048554591/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA